      <title>Yasmeen &amp; Stephen&#39;s book chapter on proteostasis dysregulation with ageing online now</title>
      <link>https://samantlab.github.io/latest-news/2022-10-28-proteostasis-ageing-chapter/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Oct 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://samantlab.github.io/latest-news/2022-10-28-proteostasis-ageing-chapter/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Our book chapter reviewing the literature on how the proteostasis network is re-wired during ageing is &lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1016/B978-0-323-91617-2.00004-3&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;online today&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thanks to &lt;a href=&#34;https://samantlab.github.io/author/yasmeen-al-mufti/&#34;&gt;Yasmeen&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://samantlab.github.io/author/stephen-cranwell&#34;&gt;Stephen&lt;/a&gt; for really getting into the weeds, and for taking charge with all the figures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This book chapter is part of the textbook, &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.sciencedirect.com/book/9780323916172/molecular-cellular-and-metabolic-fundamentals-of-human-aging&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&amp;ldquo;Molecular, Cellular, and Metabolic Fundamentals of Human Aging&amp;rdquo;&lt;/a&gt;. Thanks to the editors &lt;a href=&#34;https://evandrofanglab.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Evandro Fang&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.odont.uio.no/iob/english/research/groups/brain-and-muscle-energy/index.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Linda Bergersen&lt;/a&gt;, and Brian Gilmour for inviting us to write it!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
